OL,3,CWelsh Water fined for #250,000 sewage
OL,4,Cpollution
OL,6,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water have been fined
OL,7,F#250,000 for multiple cases of sewage
OL,8,Fpollution on the Gwent Levels and
OL,9,Fanother on a tributary of the Afon
OL,10,FLlwyd.
OL,12,FNatural Resources Wales took
OL,13,Fenforcement action after a broken
OL,14,Fsewer line discharged raw sewage into
OL,15,Fa reen and salt marsh near Magor,
OL,16,FMonmouthshire between 24th January
OL,17,F2023 and 11th January 2024
