OL,6,FThe area of salt marsh falls within
OL,7,Fthe several protected sites - a Site
OL,8,Fof Special Scientific Interest (SSSI),
OL,9,Fa Special Area of Conservation (SAC),
OL,10,FRAMSAR and Special Protection Area
OL,11,F(SPA).
OL,13,FOfficers from Natural Resources Wales
OL,14,Fwere first called to the site, near
OL,15,Fthe sea wall at Magor, on January 24
OL,16,F2023.
OL,18,FA section of the south east coast
OL,19,Fsewer line was found to have ruptured,
OL,20,Fdischarging sewage into an area known
OL,21,Fas 'back ditch".
