OL,6,FAn NRW spokesperson said the sewage
OL,7,Fwas visible over ground and throughout
OL,8,Fapproximately 400m of the tributary.
OL,10,FAt Newport Magistrates Court, the
OL,11,Fcompany was also ordered to pay costs
OL,12,Fand a surcharge of #18,320.77.
OL,14,F"For over a year, our officers
OL,15,Frecorded a pattern of recurring sewage
OL,16,Fpollution incidents in the same area,
OL,17,Fimpacting a highly protected habitat
OL,18,Fwhich is rich in plants and wildlife,
OL,19,Fincluding Saltmarsh" said John Rock,
OL,20,FNRW Operations Manager for South Wast
OL,21,FWales
