OL,6,F"Time and again we were assured that
OL,7,Fthe necessary repairs had been made,
OL,8,Fyet the pollution persisted.
OL,10,F"As well as causing considerable harm
OL,11,Fto the local environment, we found Dwr
OL,12,FCymru Welsh Water's response to the
OL,13,Fincidents to be inadequate.
OL,14,FCommunication was at times poor, and
OL,15,Fthere were unnecessary delays to their
OL,16,Fincident response procedures such as
OL,17,Fpumping and tankering away the
OL,18,Fpollution, which could have lessened
OL,19,Fthe impact.
