OL,4,Cpollution
OL,6,F"We manage a vast sewage network that
OL,7,Fspans over 36,000km of sewers and
OL,8,Fregrettably unexpected issues such as
OL,9,Fthis can arise and it's not possible
OL,10,Fto foresee theme all. The repair was
OL,11,Fhindered as we had to work around a
OL,12,Fvast wooded area and the need to
OL,13,Fpreserve the trees. This meant the
OL,14,Fsewer had to be diverted, prolonging
OL,15,Fthe incident."
OL,17,F"The second issue was on the South
OL,18,FEast Coastal Sewer. We have been
OL,19,Fexperiencing repeat issues with this
OL,20,Fsewer in recent years with the only
OL,21,Fviable solution being to replace it."
