OL,6,F"However, the estimated cost of #80
OL,7,Fmillion has meant that it has not
OL,8,Fpreviously been possible to complete
OL,9,Fthe work within our maintenance
OL,10,Fbudget."
OL,12,F"We have now, with support of NRW,
OL,13,Fsecured permission from Ofwat to raise
OL,14,Ffunds to address the issue."
OL,16,F"Each of the leaks to this main were
OL,17,Fdealt with promptly to minimise
OL,18,Fenvironmental impact."
